54
00:04:27,222 --> 00:04:27,688
Agh!

55
00:04:27,722 --> 00:04:28,555
Urrgh!

56
00:04:28,588 --> 00:04:29,955
-Good work, Ururu.

57
00:04:29,988 --> 00:04:31,022
Don't let him go.

58
