dish just for you.

267
00:14:31,294 --> 00:14:32,661
RUKIA: Wow, what's this?

268
00:14:32,694 --> 00:14:33,494
-A surprise.

269
00:14:33,528 --> 00:14:34,794
Smells good, huh?

270
00:14:34,828 --> 00:14:36,694
-Yeah, but I was on my way out.

271
