00:14:42,228 --> 00:14:44,094
[chuckles]

276
00:14:44,128 --> 00:14:45,994
-Wasn't that your tummy talking?

277
00:14:46,028 --> 00:14:48,028
-Your tummy knows
more than you do.

278
00:14:48,061 --> 00:14:49,294
You are hungry.

279
00:14:49,328 --> 00:14:51,361
-[chuckles]

280
00:14:51,394 --> 00:14:54,828
I guess I will have
some, Yuzu, since you

281
00:14:54,861 --> 00:14:56,661
went to the trouble
