bring the trays in.

285
00:15:00,528 --> 00:15:01,061
KARIN: Huh?

286
00:15:01,094 --> 00:15:04,261
Oh, sure, Yuzu.

287
00:15:04,294 --> 00:15:05,728
[water flowing]

288
00:15:12,661 --> 00:15:13,594
-[sighs]

