go somewhere, be careful.

313
00:16:00,228 --> 00:16:02,828
And be sure to bundle up.

314
00:16:02,861 --> 00:16:03,328
-All right.

315
00:16:14,728 --> 00:16:15,361
All right!

316
00:16:50,694 --> 00:16:51,294
-(WHISPERS) OK.

317
00:16:51,328 --> 00:16:52,528
There we go.

318
00:16:55,528 --> 00:16:57,928
[giggles]

319
00:16:57,961 --> 00:17:01,828
That's hard to get
used to, but here I am.

320
00:17:06,228 --> 00:17:08,628
Uh.

321
00:17:08,661 --> 00:17:11,561
Hm.

322
00:17:11,594 --> 00:17:14,494
Hm.

323
00:17:14,528 --> 00:17:17,694
I decided to say
goodbye to you, Ichigo.

324
00:17:17,728 --> 00:17:19,528
There are actually a
lot of other people

325
00:17:19,561 --> 00:17:25,128
I wanted to say goodbye to as
well, like Tatsuki, Chad, Uryu,

326
00:17:25,161 --> 00:17:27,428
Rukia, and a bunch of others.

327
00:17:27,461 --> 00:17:29,794
But I'd get in trouble if I did.

328
00:17:29,828 --> 00:17:31,361
So I had to choose.

329
00:17:35,128 --> 00:17:36,994
[breathing heavily]

330
00:17:37,028 --> 00:17:37,694
YUZU: Hrm.

331
00:17:37,728 --> 00:17:40,361
-[gasps]

332
00:17:40,394 --> 00:17:40,861
Uh.

333
00:17:45,194 --> 00:17:51,894
Oh, uh, hm.

334
00:17:51,928 --> 00:17:53,694
Oh, I get it now.

335
00:17:53,728 --> 00:17:57,861
I guess Yuzu and Karin wanted
to be close to you tonight.

336
00:17:57,894 --> 00:18:00,194
You haven't been
around much, so they

337
00:18:00,228 --> 00:18:01,728
must have really
missed you a lot.

338
00:18:01,761 --> 00:18:03,494
That's so cute.

339
00:18:03,528 --> 00:18:05,261
They brought their
plates in so they

340
00:18:05,294 --> 00:18:08,294
could have dinner
next to your bed.

341
00:18:08,328 --> 00:18:09,228
Huh?

342
00:18:09,261 --> 00:18:12,628
Wait, I just realized--
your bedroom!

343
00:18:16,494 --> 00:18:18,994
Come to think of it,
this is the first time

344
00:18:19,028 --> 00:18:25,028
I've ever been in your bathroom
