The truth is, I can't
bring myself to do it.

350
00:20:08,028 --> 00:20:09,494
[sobs]

351
00:20:12,528 --> 00:20:14,461
I'm so ashamed of myself.

352
00:20:14,494 --> 00:20:17,028
It's my last moment
with you, and I'm

353
00:20:17,061 --> 00:20:27,361
trying to-- when I
think about it, Ichigo,

354
00:20:27,394 --> 00:20:30,661
there were so many
things I wanted to do.

355
00:20:30,694 --> 00:20:32,861
I wanted to become
a school teacher.

356
00:20:32,894 --> 00:20:35,928
I wanted to become an astronaut.

357
00:20:35,961 --> 00:20:37,794
I wanted to be a baker.

358
00:20:37,828 --> 00:20:39,961
I wanted to go to a
bunch of donut shops

359
00:20:39,994 --> 00:20:41,961
and ask for one of everything.

360
00:20:41,994 --> 00:20:44,928
I even wanted to stop the
ice cream man and truck,

361
00:20:44,961 --> 00:20:50,394
and tell him to give me one
of everything he had as well.

362
00:20:50,428 --> 00:20:55,494
Haah, I wish I could have had
five different lives instead

363
00:20:55,528 --> 00:20:56,428
of one.

364
00:20:56,461 --> 00:20:58,161
Then instead of
one town, I could

365
00:20:58,194 --> 00:21:00,694
