00:21:00,728 --> 00:21:03,694
And each one would have fed me
a lifetime of different foods.

367
00:21:03,728 --> 00:21:07,928
And I would have grown up to
have five different careers.

368
00:21:07,961 --> 00:21:16,928
And in every one
of those lives, I

369
00:21:16,961 --> 00:21:20,128
would have fallen in
love with the same person

370
00:21:20,161 --> 00:21:21,594
five different times.

371
00:21:27,994 --> 00:21:29,061
Thank you, Ichigo.

372
00:21:35,128 --> 00:21:35,594
Goodbye.

